"'''Dark Hope'''" is a short story by [[August Hahn|August]] and [[Cynthia Hahn]], released on [[January 19]], [[2006]], and set within the [[Living Force (roleplaying campaign)|''Living Force'']] setting from [[Wizards of the Coast]]. Following the story arc of [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Darrus Jeht/Legends|Darrus Jeht]], it describes his meeting with [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] after the [[Battle of Kromus/Legends|Battle of Kromus]].

